content.productFullDescription: We love the durability and beauty of steel. But we didn't like the way steel bottles felt in our hands  or on our lips. So we pushed ourselves to create a better solution. Our reward was Vida. Its tapered profile and ergonomic handle make it a joy to hold. Our smooth, threadless spout replicates our Perfect Spout, a first for any steel bottle.
